Constance Seoposengwe bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa na onye na-emegide ịkpa ókè agbụrụ
Onye otu African National Congress, ọ bụ onye otu National Assembly of South Africa ugbu a.
Seoposengwe bụ onye otu United Democratic Front na onye nhazi maka South African Domestic Workers Union
Ọ rụkwara ọrụ dị ka onye nkuzi.

Mgbe ọ dị ime mgbe ọ dị afọ 22 na 1987, a tara Seoposengwe ahụhụ ma jide ya na okpukpu nke isii nke ụlọ ọrụ ndị uwe ojii Transvaal na Kimberley. Mgbe ịkpa ókè agbụrụ gasịrị, ọ ghọrọ onye otu Northern Cape Provincial Legislature na 1994, na-anọchite anya African National Congress. N'afọ 1999, a họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ osote onye isi oche nke ndị omeiwu. A họpụtara ya dị ka onye otu Executive Council (MEC) maka nchekwa na nchekwa n'afọ 2000. N'otu afọ ahụ, ọ kpughere otú ndị uwe ojii ọcha na-aṅụbiga mmanya ókè si emegbu ya n'ọnụ na ụlọ ọrụ ndị uwe ojii Hartswater.
A họpụtara Seoposengwe ka ọ bụrụ onye isi oche nke ndị omeiwu mgbe ntuli aka 2004 gasịrị, ọkwá ọ nọrọ ruo 2009.
Seoposengwe emeela mkpọsa maka ịgbanwe aha ebe na Kimberley
Ọ mere mkpọsa maka ịgbanwe aha ụlọ ọrụ ndị uwe ojii Transvaal na 2011, ma kemgbe ahụ, a gbanwere ya ka ọ bụrụ ụlọ ọrụ ndị Uwe Ojii Kimberley. N'afọ 2013, a gbara ya ajụjụ ọnụ maka ụlọ ọrụ SABC.

Seoposengwe pụtara na ndepụta ANC nke ndị na-azọ ọkwa ndị omeiwu mba na 2019. A họpụtaghị ya ka ọ bụrụ onye omeiwu na ntuli aka ahụ, Otú ọ dị, n'oge na-adịghị anya, ọ banyere na National Assembly dị ka onye nọchiri Sibongile Besani. Seoposengwe bụ onye otu Standing Committee on Auditor General na onye ọzọ so na Portfolio Committee on Human Settlements, Water and Sanitation.
